casebody.head_matter:
Christopher SHANAHAN, et al., petitioners,
v.
Alexander LORA.
No. 15-1205.
Supreme Court of the United States
March 5, 2018.
On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit. Petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit for further consideration in light of Jennings v. Rodriguez, 583 U.S ----, 138 S.Ct. 830, 200 L.E.2d 122 (2018).
